# Why This Training Matters

**Every 39 seconds, a cyber attack occurs somewhere in the world**

::: danger
**The Real Cost of Cyber Incidents:**
- Average data breach cost: {{incident_cost}}
- 68% of breaches involve human error
- 95% of successful attacks exploit employee mistakes
- Recovery time: 6-12 months on average
:::

**You are both the target and the solution**

@notes:
- Statistics updated monthly from industry reports
- Human error emphasis - not blame, but awareness
- "Target and solution" frames personal agency
- Cost figure gets attention from all departments

